"Agnis Breast Meat":
"The dishes I cooked up with the Agnis meat
you brought me were a huge hit! The breast meat
saute was especially popular. So much so, that
I'm already out of breast meat! I still have plenty
of other cuts of Agnis, so I really only need
you to bring me back some breast meat.
Do you think you could do that for me?

*Target: Agnises level 21 or higher"

"前にお願いしたアギニスの肉を使った
新作メニューが好評なの！
特に胸肉を使ったソテーが大人気で
もう全部、使い切っちゃったのよね……
他はまだ余裕があるから、できれば
胸肉だけほしいんだけど、そんなお願いを
しちゃっても大丈夫かしら？

※Lv.21～のアギニスが対象"
